data.description: Welcome to this stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom, 3-car garage home with SOLAR PANELS for the entire house that boasts immaculate design and luxurious features. The SOLAR PANELS ARE PAID OFF and generate over $3000 worth of energy annually, directly slashing your utility bills and promoting economic efficiency. It also comes with a remaining 25-year transferable warranty, ensuring you can rely on these savings for years to come. As you approach the front of the house, you are greeted by a charming front porch, perfect for relaxing and enjoying the surroundings. Upon entering the home, you are immediately captivated by the spaciousness and attention to detail. The main living area with bonus room, living room and dining room combo features an open floor plan, allowing for seamless flow and abundant natural light. The large open kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring granite countertops that exude elegance and durability. The ample counter space allows for easy meal preparation and includes a large central island, perfect for gathering and casual dining. The kitchen is equipped with top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, including a stove, refrigerator, microwave, and dishwasher. Throughout the home, ceramic tile floors create a clean ambiance. The master suite is a sanctuary of relaxation and indulgence. The spacious bedroom provides a tranquil retreat, complete with a walk-in closet for ample storage. The master bathroom boasts a luxurious feel with granite counters, dual sinks, a deep soaking tub, and a separate glass-enclosed shower. The remaining three bedrooms are equally well-appointed, offering comfortable living spaces for family members or guests. Each bedroom is thoughtfully designed and includes spacious closets and large windows for abundant natural light. All windows come with custom blinds for privacy. The home also features two additional well-appointed bathrooms, each with stylish fixtures, granite counters, and modern amenities. These bathrooms are designed with both elegance and functionality in mind. As you make your way to the back of the home, you'll discover a screened porch, providing a tranquil space to enjoy the outdoors while being protected from insects and the elements. Metered Sprinkler system will keep your yard lush and green. To accommodate your vehicles and storage needs, the home features a spacious three-car garage. This area provides ample space for parking, as well as additional storage options. Don't miss the opportunity to tour this remarkable property and envision the possibilities it holds for you and your family.
